\[ 5 + 6 + 4 = 15 \text{ hours} \]

Finally, the total time spent hovering over all regions over the two days is:
\[ 9 + 15 = 24 \text{ hours} \]

Thus, the total time it took the plane to hover over Mountain time, Central time, and Eastern time in the two days is \(\boxed{24}\). 
