   Jon gets 50 visits per hour.

2. **Calculate the number of hours in a day:**
   The website operates 24 hours a day.

3. **Calculate the number of visits per day:**
   \[
   \text{Visits per day} = \text{Visits per hour} \times \text{Hours per day} = 50 \times 24 = 1200
   \]

