\[
\text{Total revenue from iPads} = 20 \times 900 = 18000
\]

**Step 3: Calculate the total revenue from Apple TVs.**
The store sold 80 Apple TVs at an average cost of $200 per Apple TV.
\[
\text{Total revenue from Apple TVs} = 80 \times 200 = 16000
\]

