   \[
   \text{Number of girls} = \frac{60}{2} = 30
   \]

5. **Calculate the total number of boys and girls:**
   \[
   \text{Total number of boys and girls} = \text{Number of boys} + \text{Number of girls} = 10 + 30 = 40
   \]

